The paper deals with video annotation using image processing algorithms and Hidden Markov Models, which are commonly used in computer vision and machine learning. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves modeling and classification, which are core topics in cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper discusses the reduction of manual annotation labor, which is relevant to cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction). Finally, the paper deals with video datasets, which falls under cs.MM (Multimedia).
